&lt;li&gt;Ensure execution of export control audits, restricted party screening, and voluntary disclosure management to DDTC and BIS; maintain accountability for timely and accurate reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure export control training programs meet regulatory requirements under 22 C.F.R. Part 122 and 15 C.F.R. Part 762, whether delivered internally or through an external provider.&lt;/li&gt;
